data.description: This unique two story home features a spacious master bedroom and bath upstairs. The master suite includes generous storage space, walk-in shower, double vanity, enclosed water closet and large walk-in closet. Also, the upstairs includes two bedrooms, bonus room, full bath and laundry for added convenience. The bedroom with full bath on the first floor is perfect for hosting family and friends. Entering from the garage you will find a large walk-in pantry, open kitchen with ample counter space and sizable center island with a stainless steel single-basin sink and dishwasher. Enjoy an open concept layout connecting the kitchen, dining and great room.
